channel.title: Im not sure what to do
channel.description:
Im on the "how to make\add your own custom item guide" And im stuck on this STEP 9
"After Compiling Run it and Enter your Server. Once in you must say Code:
add model 12056 add model 12057
It should say Model Successfully found.
Once it says that then your item is ready just do ::pickup (whatever you numbered your item) (amount)
Then BAM your first ever item Big Grin"
What does it mean "say this" and it will add the models, what do i do exactly?
